metadata.name: Carousel
metadata.description:
I close my eyes, but it doesn't help. In the darkness, the fire burns even brighter.
This is a digital life of great work canvas oil 120 * 80cm.
The original of this work was exhibited at various exhibitions.
2022 - Edition 1/1 GIF
There is such a children's song:
"Carousel, carousel begins the story.
These are fairy tales, songs and fun!
Carousel, carousel is a joy for us,
Take a ride on our carousel! "
And I painted my experience and the image (metaphor) of burning time and childhood. We become a participant in this picture and a viewer, like these girls who may have done all this.
